import { Injectable } from "@angular/core";
import { DecoratorTypesService } from "src/app/featureManagement/decoratorsVariationPointManagement/decorator-types.service";

@Injectable({
    providedIn: "root"
})
export class BringToBackService {
    public prepareBringToBackIcon(): HTMLImageElement {
        const bringToBackIcon = "data:image/svg+xml;base64,";
        const img = new Image();
        img.src = bringToBackIcon;
        return img;
    }
    public bringToBack(): fabric.ControlMouseEventHandler {
        return (eventData: MouseEvent, transform: fabric.Transform): boolean => {
            const boardCanvas = transform.target.canvas;
            if (boardCanvas !== undefined) {
                if ("_objects" in transform.target) {
                    (transform.target as unknown as fabric.Canvas)._objects.forEach(puzzle => boardCanvas.sendToBack(puzzle));
                    return true;
                }
                else {
                    boardCanvas.sendToBack(transform.target);
                }
            }
            else {
                console.log("Error: canvas is undefined - cant send puzzle to back!");
            }
            return true;
        };
    }
}
